lead_paragraph: Chancellor George Osborne will announce a pre-election budget on Wednesday that is likely to offer some tax relief to voters but will stick closely to his tough decade-long plan to fix the public finances.

headline.main: Osborne to Stick to Austerity Course With New Budget Plan
